headline: RMD Q1 Earnings Call: Margin Expansion and Demand Generation Initiatives Define Quarter
summary: Medical device company ResMed (NYSE:RMD) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 7.9% year on year to $1.29 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.37 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
